    "description": {
      "value": "\r\n<p class=\"source\"><b>Source</b>: <a title=\"PZO9455\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1601257325/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=1601257325&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=httpwwwd20pfs-20&amp;linkId=RTYNEYJM7WKLVCFB\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PZO9455</a></p>\r\n<p><b>Price</b> 25 gp; <b>Weight</b> 10 lbs.</p>\r\n<p>This wood-and-leather <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/goods-and-services/animals-animal-gear#TOC-Harness\">harness</a> fits over clothing or armor and provides small handles and footrests across your back and along the sides of your legs and arms. While wearing a handle <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/goods-and-services/animals-animal-gear#TOC-Harness\">harness</a>, you automatically succeed at checks to aid an adjacent ally of your size or smaller with <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/climb\">Climb</a> or <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/ride\">Ride</a> checks, or <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/acrobatics\">Acrobatics</a> checks to balance on narrow surfaces or uneven ground. A handle <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/goods-and-services/animals-animal-gear#TOC-Harness\">harness's</a> ungainly construction gives you a -2 penalty on <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/escape-artist\">Escape Artist</a> checks.</p>\r\n\r\n"
